{"id":96073,"type":6,"name":"Everybody Hates Chris (Season 1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/47/8a/96073_RxAeB.jpg","rating":{"total":4,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":0,"7":1,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":7},"summary":"13岁的黑人小孩克里斯（泰勒·詹姆斯·威廉姆 Tyler James Williams 饰）生活在纽约布鲁克林区，家中有做好几份低等工拼命养家、极度抠门的老爸朱利叶斯（泰瑞·克鲁斯 Terry Crews 饰），有虚荣、能干的大嗓门老妈罗谢尔（蒂琪娜·阿诺 Tichin a Arnold 饰），还有一对麻烦的弟妹德鲁（特昆·里奇蒙德 Tequan Richmond 饰）和唐娅（Imani Hakim 饰）。到了上学年龄，克里斯被严格的老妈送入白人学校，不出所料受尽欺侮，但也有幸交到一个好朋友——因瘦弱苍白同样要做受气包的格雷戈（文森特·马特拉 Vincent Martella 饰），每天从家里到学校同样吵闹和无奈，克里斯始终用一种无所谓的自嘲精神面对这一切…… \r\n　　本剧里面“克里斯”的原型是艾美奖得主、喜剧明星克里斯·洛克（Chris Rock），并由他本人亲自担任独白。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>人人都恨克里斯 第一季</li><li><span>集数: </span>22</li><li><span>开始: </span>2005-09-22</li><li><span>结束: </span>2006-05-11</li><li><span>类型: </span>喜剧</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>美国</li><li><span>语言: </span>英语</li><li><span>每集长: </span>20分钟</li><li><span>电视台: </span>UPN/The CW sitcom</li><li><span>imdb_id: </span>tt0460637</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":6,"doing":1,"on_hold":2},"tags":[{"name":"美剧","count":4},{"name":"喜剧","count":3}],"eps":[{"id":368674,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/368674","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":368675,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/368675","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":368676,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/368676","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":368677,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/368677","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":368678,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/368678","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":368679,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/368679","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status